  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13092310/inghams-winter-838x330.jpg" alt="New Year ski Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/29f2f005c84547f8baa34cdaaba3c3e3" /></p>
<p>New Year ski holidays are all about celebration and parties. Fireworks, good times and lots of laughter. Nothing says 'let's make some memories' like a day of skiing down fresh powder and some untouched trails.</p>
<p>Whether you want to celebrate the New Year by hitting the slopes, indulging in some après-ski or relaxing in a luxury chalet, we have ski holidays to suit.</p>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13089361/climate-action-plan-hero-838x330.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2a04a7d8f96e4ed095539e0430ce5c35" /></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">New Year ski departure dates</h2>
<p>skiing at New Year is extremely popular and the best resorts sell out quickly so we advise that you book as early as possible, especially if you're looking for a <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalets">catered ski chalet over New Year.</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December" class="c-btn">View December deals</a></p>
<h2>Best New Year accommodation</h2>
<p><strong>See in the New Year on the slopes - </strong>Discover our favourite hotels, perfect for a New Year Ski holiday. </p>
<div id="top" class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4fed39a49ebb49d183e319e12f57a5ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4fed39a49ebb49d183e319e12f57a5ae}" title="Hotel Arlberg">Hotel Arlberg</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13092320/hotel-arlberg-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/917d6136b4924b55b342e2031f97971e" /></p>
<p>Conveniently located near the Nasserein gondola and a short walk from the centre of town, this family-run hotel offers a home away from home and excellent leisure facilities.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" class="c-btn">St. Anton - Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/06ae3dbdf9ac4a768e0e460ffe477363" href="/{localLink:umb://document/06ae3dbdf9ac4a768e0e460ffe477363}?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel Prieure" data-anchor="?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Hotel Prieure</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13092321/hotel-prieure-chamonix-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a288468ca58c42f0906e9d905487550f" /></p>
<p>Located in the centre of Chamonix, the hotel is decorated in a contemporary wooden chalet style. The cosy bar and lounge with fireplace is a great place to unwind after a day of skiing.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" class="c-btn">Chamonix - France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c86924ec947441bbda313b26e672955" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c86924ec947441bbda313b26e672955}?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Q Hotel Maria Theresia" data-anchor="?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Hotel Maria Theresia</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13092322/hotel-maria-theresa-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/27a7d9c8537443268d74bbd6daf1710d" /></p>
<p>A stylish hotel located in the centre and a 4 minute walk from the Hahnenkamm gondola. The hotel has a traditional and contemporary interior, excellent cuisine and an extensive spa area.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/daebb810f1b948b9acb0b1555405cdac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/daebb810f1b948b9acb0b1555405cdac}" class="c-btn">Kitzbuhel - Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec}?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Levi Hotel Spa" data-anchor="?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Levi Spa Hotel</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13092323/levi-spa-hotel-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7238cb36adb14737a1f9d78f36c7012e" /></p>
<p>Set in a quiet and convenient location, just minutes from the ski lifts and village centre, this beautiful hotel has excellent spa and recreation facilities, making it a perfect hotel for families and couples alike.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" class="c-btn">Levi - Lapland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/836fe8a77b2c4f6eb30fa8120b4326b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/836fe8a77b2c4f6eb30fa8120b4326b5}?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Residence Cassiopee" data-anchor="?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Residence Cassiopee</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13092319/residence-cassiopee-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1d5501eba1814c43ae7a2c18e357c367" /></p>
<p>Located right in the centre of Belle Plagne, you can ski to within 50 metres of the apartments. Each apartment even has it's own sauna. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4}" class="c-btn">La Plagne - France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cb76241406db44c7b6930c63fc375ad3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb76241406db44c7b6930c63fc375ad3}?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Chalet Fauner A" data-anchor="?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Chalet Fauner A</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13091064/chalet-fauner-a-st-anton-314x193.jpg" alt="Chalet Fauner A" data-udi="umb://media/e497a08b021c4f78ba9a984ca1a99c15" /></p>
<p><span>Located in a peaceful setting, Chalet Fauner overlooks the wonderful forested slopes of Rendl. This beautiful chalet is ideal for group stays.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" class="c-btn">St. Anton - Austria</a><span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36}" class="c-btn">View New Years Eve ski deals</a></div>
<p><a href="#top" data-anchor="#top">Back to top of page</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Best New Year resorts</h2>
<p><strong>Where to ski at New Year - </strong>We’ve hand-picked some of the best snow-sure resorts for New Year’s Eve skiing in Europe. Check out our snowy new year’s eve destinations.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St.Anton - Austria</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092311/st-anton-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2161625df1ee46d0807b96d78b5287da" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Known for it's après ski scene, St Anton provides the perfect place to ring in the new year with great food, drinks, and an incredible atmosphere. <span style="font-weight: 400;"><span class="s3"></span></span></li>
<li>Don't miss St. Anton illuminated,<span> an incredible laser and sound show right in St. Anton village centre on New Years Eve. </span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" class="c-btn">View St.Anton</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4}" title="La Plagne">La Plagne - France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092312/la-plagne-town-view-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f8caa470565c45d8835e3d0de6188a4f" /></p>
<ul>
<li>La Plagne is a popular French ski resort that offers aprés and nightlife. There is something for everyone, from quiet drinks to late-night party venues.</li>
<li>On New Year’s Eve, a party is held at the bottom of the piste in Bellcote. Many bars hold their own parties and restaurants often have special menus. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4}" class="c-btn">View La Plagne</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes - France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092313/tignes-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6104970c22de40819ddaf782c8b8f606" /></p>
<ul>
<li>If you love skiing or snowboarding, the Espace Killy is perfect for a New Year's celebration due its high-altitude location, there's great snow.</li>
<li>You can take advantage of several slopes during your trip in Tignes and neighbouring Val d'Isere, as well as all of the lively nightlife that comes with staying in a European mountain village.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" class="c-btn">View Tignes</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia - Italy</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092314/cervinia-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6ca44527d9394a5d9f08368b0accc2fe" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Celebrate the New Year with a big party and fireworks in Cervinia. Cervinia is a small but popular resort on the Alpi Pennine, which overlooks the Mont Blanc Massif and has a long skiing area over the Italian border to Switzerland. </li>
<li>The resort is renowned for its excellent snow conditions, beautiful scenery and warm welcoming atmosphere.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" class="c-btn">View Cervinia</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix - France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 208px;" src="/media/13092315/chamonix-400x208.jpg?width=400&amp;height=208" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0868fb6d462f483d883b3de2acd9b88e" /></p>
<ul>
<li>With stunning views over Mont Blanc and the Aiguille du Midi, Chamonix offers a unique New Year’s experience.</li>
<li>Plenty of restaurants, après ski bars and nightclubs put on brilliant New Year’s Eve celebrations. As is the tradition in Chamonix on New Year’s Eve, everyone gathers in the town centre for a countdown, firework display and plenty of drinking!</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" class="c-btn">View Chamonix</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka - Lapland</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092316/saariselka-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0434adb825f446319db557f312d1adf7" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Visit Lapland for NYE</strong> - Located high up in the Arctic circle of Finland, Saariselka is like no other ski resort in Europe. Snow-capped mountains, herds of reindeer and a frozen Arctic landscape - it's so much more than a ski resort.</li>
<li>Stay at the unique <a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Muotka Wilderness Hotel</a> and enjoy a<span> bonfire, midnight fireworks and a glass of sparkling wine on New Year's Eve.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" class="c-btn">View Lapland</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
